summary: “I didn’t know if you knew, so I’m taking this chance to say...” @taylorswift  ♡  Taylor, I’m seeing you Sunday, July 22nd, and...
body:
“I didn’t know if you knew, so I’m taking this chance to say…” @taylorswift  ♡

Taylor, I’m seeing you Sunday, July 22nd, and I just wanted to say thank you for being you, always. You make me feel that it’s okay to be myself, too, something I’ve struggled with for as long as I can remember. I’ve been your fan since I was a young girl, and have grown up with you. Your heart never fails to leave me feeling warm, and your words never fail to leave me feeling comforted. I love youuuuu so, btw, your new Bazaar cover is so vintage and I adore it!! ♡
